# üö® MANDATORY: Catalog Field Selection (Check FIRST Before Creating ANY FieldDef)

**ALWAYS check catalog fields FIRST. Only create custom FieldDefs when no catalog field fits.**

## Quick Field Selection Table

| If your field represents... | USE THIS CATALOG FIELD | Import Path | NOT |
|----------------------------|------------------------|-------------|-----|
| **Duration/time span** | `DurationField` | `'@cardstack/catalog/fields/time/duration'` | ‚ùå `NumberField` for minutes |
| **Star rating (1-5, 1-10)** | `RatingField` | `'@cardstack/catalog/fields/rating'` | ‚ùå `NumberField` |
| **Quantity with +/- controls** | `QuantityField` | `'@cardstack/catalog/fields/quantity'` | ‚ùå `NumberField` |
| **Image upload** | `ImageField` | `'@cardstack/catalog/fields/image'` | ‚ùå `StringField` for URL |
| **Multiple images** | `MultipleImageField` | `'@cardstack/catalog/fields/multiple-image'` | ‚ùå `containsMany(StringField)` |
| **Date selection** | `DateField` | `'@cardstack/catalog/fields/date'` | ‚ùå `StringField` |
| **Time selection** | `TimeField` | `'@cardstack/catalog/fields/time'` | ‚ùå `StringField` |
| **Date + time** | `DatetimeField` | `'@cardstack/catalog/fields/date-time'` | ‚ùå Two separate fields |
| **Date range** | `DateRangeField` | `'@cardstack/catalog/fields/date/date-range'` | ‚ùå Two DateFields |
| **Time range** | `TimeRangeField` | `'@cardstack/catalog/fields/time/time-range'` | ‚ùå Two TimeFields |
| **Number with visualization** | `NumberField` + presentation | `'@cardstack/catalog/fields/number'` | ‚ùå Custom component |
| **Recurring schedule** | `RecurringPatternField` | `'@cardstack/catalog/fields/recurring-pattern'` | ‚ùå Custom logic |
| **Audio playback** | `AudioField` | `'@cardstack/catalog/fields/audio'` | ‚ùå `StringField` for URL |
| **Precise timestamp** | `DatetimeStampField` | `'@cardstack/catalog/fields/datetime-stamp'` | ‚ùå `StringField` |
| **Birthday/anniversary** | `MonthDayField` | `'@cardstack/catalog/fields/date/month-day'` | ‚ùå Two NumberFields |
| **Fiscal quarter** | `QuarterField` | `'@cardstack/catalog/fields/date/quarter'` | ‚ùå `StringField` |
| **Day of month** | `DayField` | `'@cardstack/catalog/fields/date/day'` | ‚ùå `NumberField` |
| **Year selection** | `YearField` | `'@cardstack/catalog/fields/date/year'` | ‚ùå `NumberField` |
| **Month selection** | `MonthField` | `'@cardstack/catalog/fields/date/month'` | ‚ùå `NumberField` |
| **Week of year** | `WeekField` | `'@cardstack/catalog/fields/date/week'` | ‚ùå `NumberField` |
| **Relative time** | `RelativeTimeField` | `'@cardstack/catalog/fields/time/relative-time'` | ‚ùå `StringField` |
| **Named period** | `TimePeriodField` | `'@cardstack/catalog/fields/time-period'` | ‚ùå `StringField` |

## Common Domain ‚Üí Field Mappings

| Domain/App Type | Common Fields Needed |
|-----------------|---------------------|
| **Recipe/Cooking** | `DurationField` (prep/cook time), `RatingField` (difficulty), `QuantityField` (servings), `ImageField` (photos) |
| **E-commerce** | `ImageField`/`MultipleImageField` (products), `RatingField` (reviews), `QuantityField` (stock), `NumberField` (price with stat/gauge) |
| **Fitness/Health** | `DurationField` (workout length), `NumberField` (calories with progress-bar), `DateField` (workout date), `RatingField` (intensity) |
| **Music/Audio** | `AudioField` (tracks), `DurationField` (track length), `ImageField` (album art), `RatingField` (stars) |
| **Events/Booking** | `DatetimeField` (event time), `DateRangeField` (booking period), `QuantityField` (attendees), `ImageField` (venue) |
| **Task Management** | `DateField` (due date), `RatingField` (priority), `DurationField` (time estimate), `NumberField` (progress with progress-bar) |
| **Content/Blog** | `DateField` (publish date), `ImageField` (featured image), `MultipleImageField` (gallery), `DurationField` (read time) |
| **Finance** | `NumberField` (amounts with stat/gauge), `DateField` (transaction date), `DateRangeField` (reporting period), `QuarterField` (fiscal quarter) |
| **Calendar/Scheduling** | `RecurringPatternField` (repeating events), `DatetimeField` (appointments), `TimeRangeField` (availability), `DurationField` (meeting length) |
| **Education** | `DateField` (assignment due), `YearField` (graduation), `QuarterField` (semester), `RatingField` (grade), `DurationField` (course length) |

---

# Custom Fields Library

Boxel provides a rich set of custom field types beyond the base primitives. These fields offer specialized input/display behaviors, configuration options, and presentation modes.

## Import Pattern

Custom fields are imported from the catalog realm:

```gts
// Date & Time Fields
import DateField from '@cardstack/catalog/fields/date';
import TimeField from '@cardstack/catalog/fields/time';
import DatetimeField from '@cardstack/catalog/fields/date-time';
import DatetimeStampField from '@cardstack/catalog/fields/datetime-stamp';
import DayField from '@cardstack/catalog/fields/date/day';
import YearField from '@cardstack/catalog/fields/date/year';
import MonthField from '@cardstack/catalog/fields/date/month';
import MonthYearField from '@cardstack/catalog/fields/date/month-year';
import WeekField from '@cardstack/catalog/fields/date/week';
import DateRangeField from '@cardstack/catalog/fields/date/date-range';
import TimeRangeField from '@cardstack/catalog/fields/time/time-range';
import DurationField from '@cardstack/catalog/fields/time/duration';
import RelativeTimeField from '@cardstack/catalog/fields/time/relative-time';
import MonthDayField from '@cardstack/catalog/fields/date/month-day';
import QuarterField from '@cardstack/catalog/fields/date/quarter';
import RecurringPatternField from '@cardstack/catalog/fields/recurring-pattern';
import TimePeriodField from '@cardstack/catalog/fields/time-period';

// Number Fields
import NumberField from '@cardstack/catalog/fields/number';
import RatingField from '@cardstack/catalog/fields/rating';
import QuantityField from '@cardstack/catalog/fields/quantity';

// Image Fields
import ImageField from '@cardstack/catalog/fields/image';
import MultipleImageField from '@cardstack/catalog/fields/multiple-image';

// Audio Fields
import AudioField from '@cardstack/catalog/fields/audio';
```

---

## Best Practices

1. **Choose the right field type** - Don't use DatetimeField when DateField suffices
2. **Configure appropriate units** - Example: DurationField without months avoids ambiguity
3. **Use presentation modes** - Match visualization to context (dashboards ‚Üí stat/gauge)
